{"tid":1261753,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"卻奧斯話C朗離隊人人開心","createTime":"2019-06-27T11:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:39:25.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"974f610b323e80b9b61fc410e546e16cb5138417","tid":1261753,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"卻奧斯話C朗離隊人人開心<br />\n<br />\n雖然皇馬的隊友十分想念C朗拿度，不過卻奧斯承認C朗轉去祖記，對於兩家球會的所有人都是好事。<br />\n<br />\n卻奧斯解釋說道：「如果說大家不想念C朗是奇怪的事，畢竟他射入這麼多重要入球。但他轉會對大家都好，他可以有新挑戰，皇馬又收回一大筆轉會費。」（<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=F8rBtbRGk5TlA8%2FYPnv0dosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=282ad510\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>）"},{"pid":"1f2ee400aa015c5b5f6260b206c8161600e71de9","tid":1261753,"uid":815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:49:41.000Z","msg":"鳩硬蛇收工啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6b9d25ee58f865a95143e43ea5806356f434e4","tid":1261753,"uid":132189,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir有冇收到風清doj"},{"pid":"bb883607358f9d78d4474a501e9daf9ba01fa22d","tid":1261753,"uid":99856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:54:11.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir 我好支持你 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驚你睇唔明 翻譯番：汪汪汪汪 汪汪 汪汪汪"},{"pid":"f41cfb74ae5e728efe450caa2ad0d24cae251366","tid":1261753,"uid":1823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"鳩硬sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61fbc56d465b72295f3f8090eaebdd8197fbd514","tid":1261753,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:56:32.000Z","msg":"到夏神上門佢就笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces